{
    "name": "Medusa Head",
    "type": "monster",
    "sections": [
        {
            "name": "Description",
            "html": "Beheaded are f loating skulls or severed heads whose bodies have long since abandoned them, either in the moment of death or long after. Reanimated via dark magic, these horrors are usually created as mindless sentinels for dungeons or lairs. Beheaded silently hover at about eye-level, often making them the last thing a casual wanderer or careless villager in an infested area ever sees."
        }
    ],
